Lappeenranta.title: Lappeenranta
Lappeenranta.byline: The City of Lappeenranta (population 73,000 in 2023) is the economic and cultural centre of Finnish South Karelia.

Lapu-Lapu.title: Lapu-Lapu
Lapu-Lapu.byline: Lapu-Lapu is an island city of Cebu Province in the Philippines, part of Metro Cebu.

Laponia.title: Laponia
Laponia.byline: Laponia is a national park system of and a UNESCO World Heritage site in Norrbotten County, in the Lappland province in northern Sweden.

Lapinjärvi.title: Lapinjärvi
Lapinjärvi.byline: Lapinjärvi (Swedish: Lappträsk) is a municipality in Uusimaa.
